2007-12-29 13:31  Rocky Bernstein

	* trunk/ChangeLog, rdebug, trunk/cli/ruby-debug/command.rb,
	  trunk/ext/ChangeLog, trunk/lib/ChangeLog, trunk/test/helper.rb,
