2007-05-17 14:03  Rocky Bernstein

	* rdebug: -d option: turns on $DEBUG
	  -v option: print version number, then turn on verbose mode
	  ($VERBOSE)
	  --verbose turns on verbose mode ($VERBOSE)
	  --version works the same
	  --verbose turns on verbose mode ($VERBOSE)

